00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:40,880
No one checks there.

289
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,760
You got the goods off the train?

290
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,080
When the train slowed down

291
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,160
near Halan's outskirts,

292
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:50,440
I tossed the package out the window.

293
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:53,720
