6 months ago? In-city transport method]

319
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:34,960
We were right.

320
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:36,280
These drug dealers

321
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:38,360
are selling both Red Dragon and meth.

322
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:42,320
But according to the police in Huazhou,

323
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,760
Hao sells everything

324
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:47,520
