325
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,400
But he has never touched meth.

326
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:54,560
Where on earth is the supplier of meth?

327
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:58,600
The murder case

328
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,080
is basically solved.

329
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:04,520
Hao from Huazhou asked Chen Liang
