337
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:20,440
To protect the entire

338
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,760
Red Dragon

339
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,840
operation,

340
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:24,920
Chen Liang was also silenced.

341
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:28,800
The drug dealers in Huazhou
are all ruthless.

342
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:30,240
They can't bear

343
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:32,480
being tricked by their partners.

344
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:34,880
