381
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,720
Erjin.

382
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:09,880
I beg you, Erjin.

383
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:10,680
I'll give you all the money.

384
00:20:10,800 --> 00:20:11,680
Erjin.

