firmly established yourself in Halan.

419
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:06,080
We can't use the train channel anymore.

420
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:08,040
Don't worry.

421
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:09,920
I'll find a new channel
as soon as possible.

422
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,200
You know,

423
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,880
the situation is tense right now.

424
00:22:13,120 --> 00:22:15,440
