your guy everywhere.

446
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:12,200
If he betrays us,

447
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:14,520
our whole channel will be exposed.

448
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,280
Hao,

449
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:19,160
give me a photo of Liang.

450
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,560
I'll handle this perfectly.

451
00:23:21,960 --> 00:23:23,720
Then we can continue to make a fortune.

452
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:24,440
How about that?

453
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,600
Once Liang is dead,

454
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:28,400
this will become a mystery
without a lead.

455
00:23:28,760 --> 00:23:30,640
I know what you are thinking.

456
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:33,080
You're afraid that if this gets out,

457
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:36,000
