458
00:23:36,760 --> 00:23:37,600
Hao,

459
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:40,720
we are in the same boat.

460
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:43,720
Liang is from Huazhou.

461
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,360
Once the police in Halan catch him

462
